\hat{A}^{\mu} \hat{A}_{\alpha}\, \pi^{\alpha}_{\mu}
= A_* \left(2 \hat{A}^2 - A_*^2\right) \left(2 \; {\cal B}^{\alpha}_{\mu} K^{\mu}_{\alpha} 
+ 3 \;  {\cal B}^{\alpha \beta}_{\mu \nu} K^{\mu}_{\alpha} K^{\nu}_{\beta} \right).
